{"article_id":"uCtGXBR6Y5viNbTp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After waiting days to hear from Christine Blasey Ford , the woman","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"alleging","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh sexually assaulted her","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"when they were both teenagers ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Ford 's lawyers sent Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"( R-Iowa )","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"a letter Tuesday night","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"making clear","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that she would n't appear at Monday 's hearing","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"unless and until the FBI investigated her claim first .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` She will talk with the committee , ''","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Ford 's lawyer Lisa Banks told CNN 's Anderson Cooper .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"`` She is not prepared to talk in public on Monday . ''","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Within an hour , Grassley had responded","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"-- making very clear","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that it was Monday or never for Ford .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"`` Dr. Ford 's testimony would reflect her personal knowledge and memory of events , ''","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"said Grassley in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"`` Nothing","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the FBI or any other investigator does","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"would have any bearing on what Dr. Ford tells the committee ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"so there is no reason for any further delay . ''","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Grassley 's gambit was quickly backed by several senators","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"who had been the most uneasy about the prospect","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"of moving forward with a vote on Kavanaugh 's confirmation","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"without hearing from Ford first .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"`` After learning of the allegation ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Chairman @ ChuckGrassley took immediate action","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to ensure","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"both Dr. Ford and Judge Kavanaugh have the opportunity","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to be heard , in public or private , ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"tweeted Tennessee Sen. Bob Corker","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"( R ) .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"`` Republicans extended a hand in good faith .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"If we do n't hear from both sides on Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"let 's vote . ''","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Added Republican Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake :","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"`` I implore Dr. Ford to accept the invitation for Monday , in a public or private setting . ''","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"And with that , the game of chicken was formally joined :","depth":2},{"id":39,"text":"On one side , Ford","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"insisting","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"without an investigation ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"there can be no full hearing on the accusations .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"On the other , Senate Republicans and the White House ,","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"arguing","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"that they are offering Ford a platform","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to tell her story","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"but noting","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that the opportunity has an expiration date .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":87,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":71,"right":86,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":62,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":59,"right":61,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":53,"right":58,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":53,"left":0,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":1,"right":51,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":51,"le